%h1 What are you working on right now?

- if @time_slot
  %p
    You started working on
    %strong= @time_slot.project
    =relevant_time(@time_slot.start)
    \.

- form_for :time_slot, :url => timeline_path, :html => {:method => :put} do |f|
  - @projects.each do |p|
    = f.radio_button :project_id, p.id
    = f.label "project_id_#{p.id}", p.name
    %br
  = f.submit "Track time!"